com.upsight.mediation.mraid

Interface MRAIDNativeFeatureListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MRaidPostroll

    public interface MRAIDNativeFeatureListener
    A listener for MRAIDView/MRAIDInterstitial to listen for notifications when the following native features are requested from a creative: * make a phone call * add a calendar entry * play a video (external) * open a web page in a browser * store a picture * send an SMS If you don't implement this interface, the default for supporting these features in the creative will be false.
